### create artical
POST http://localhost:4000/author-api/article
Content-Type: application/json

{
     "title":"JAVA2",
     "category":"programming",
     "content":"thi is java  article"
}

### read artical by author
GET http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles

### read artical by user
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/article/69b6e1067faf15e69e2f603d

### update the artical
PUT http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
     "articleId":"69c4ec4d36b35f8fa20e3300",
     "title":"Python",
     "category":"programming",
     "content":"updated content"
}
### soft delete the article

PATCH http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/69c4ec4d36b35f8fa20e3300/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ 
     "isArticalActive": true
}


### get article by user
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/articles

### add comment to article

PUT http://localhost:4000/user-api/articleComment 
Content-Type: application/json

{
     "articleId":"69c4ec4d36b35f8fa20e3300",
     "comment":"good"
}


